{"tid":130820,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱個Mk妹逼我食個多醬嘅麥樂雞包...","createTime":"2017-02-22T15:45:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T03:15:55.000Z","uid":51346,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f26c940ba2d526061755982b8b35e599890b5e15","tid":130820,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T15:45:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=我 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=mk妹收銀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：下位丫 食咩呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：麥樂雞包係度食 (諗住一陣就咁擸個包就走)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:一個麥樂雞包 多醬？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：唔駛啦(我心諗多乜春醬呀，邊個字令你聯想到要多醬呀)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：11蚊丫<br />\n<br />\n咁我就拍落去啦 點知見到<br />\n麥樂雞包 <br />\n多醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n外賣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前睇過m記post話咁樣嗌會特別整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />麻煩到人(加料)<br />\n<br />\n究竟點解個mk妹要逼我食個多醬嘅麥樂雞包呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e67c9eb98c45827481cd3ba309f26945d238d1","tid":130820,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T15:46:12.000Z","msg":"麥樂雞包？有無相？"},{"pid":"4e6581673e6492646a2f6b94f87004a0b4ddc3dc","tid":130820,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T15:58:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>麥樂雞包？有無相？</blockquote><br />\n食完 張單就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af6ada59e6e55305b9f3291b877edf1b3270b7d","tid":130820,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T16:06:31.000Z","msg":"Mk妹？有無相？"},{"pid":"383b36a6df4b1f7457386f8c604d9f6aaf01dd28","tid":130820,"